fulltitle: Arturo Sandoval - First Encounter with the Day

description:
The first thing Arturo Sandoval does every day is sit down at the piano. In this video, Sandoval talks about his instrument and how starting the morning with music makes every day better. 

Buy Arturo Sandoval's music at J.W. Pepper: https://www.jwpepper.com/sheet-music/search.jsp?redirect=2017-arturo-sandoval-music&pageview=grid-view&utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=jazz-100&utm_content=sandoval-video5

Read the blog: http://blogs.jwpepper.com/index.php/jazz-100-arturo-sandoval-bringing-latin-jazz-to-the-world?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=jazz&utm_content=sandoval-video5

Created by: J.W. Pepper & Son, Inc.
Produced by: Ian McLoughlin & Rocco Richardson
Filmed by: Rocco Richardson, Tim Sugrue & Mark Patterson
Edited by: Rocco Richardson
Interviewer: Al Moretti
Featuring: Arturo Sandoval, http://arturosandoval.com
YouTube Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCnPkqxFhnwmXA1DQKdvRMUw/feed
Filmed on location and in cooperation with Longwood Gardens https://longwoodgardens.org
Additional footage provided by Paul The Trombonist 
http://www.paulthetrombonist.com
YouTube Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/PaulTheTrombonist
